headline: US Space Force Successfully Launches L3Harris-Built NTS-3 Satellite
summary: MELBOURNE, Fla., August 13, 2025--The L3Harris-built (NYSE: LHX) advanced Navigation Technology Satellite-3 (NTS-3) has successfully launched from Cape Canaveral Space Force Station on a United Launch Alliance (ULA) Vulcan rocket.

headline: The Zacks Analyst Blog Highlights Lockheed Martin's, Boeing and L3Harris Technologies
